              },
              {
                "item_values": [],
                "key": "Type",
                "string_values": [
                  "<p>Mystical Beasts </p>"
                ]
              },
              {
                "item_values": [],
                "key": "Tutorial",
                "string_values": [
                  "<p>A Qucusaurus whose extraordinary form is a result of being unable to withstand the great power it has been granted. It will fly into the air during combat and enter the \"Golden Flame\" energy-gathering form, creating a shield around itself and launching a Flamewind Feather towards the ground that summons a flamewind. If you cannot destroy the Flamewind Feather before the Qucusaurus dives down into it, the creature will use a Phlogiston Current to return to the skies. This will persist until it is exhausted and returns to its original form. It seems, then, that <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 225, 75)\">destroying the Flamewind Feather using Elements that react with Pyro</span> may be the key to victory...</p>"
                ]
              }
            ]
          }
        }
      ]
    },
